      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0586P0-02247'>
        <a name='S5LV0586P0_19980223_GCR_137'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gareth-williams' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0586P0_19980223_GCR_137' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gareth Williams' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
